 Naomi , 44 , and 24-year-old Jourdan have been unveiled as the faces of Burberry 's new eyewear range , the Gabardine collection .
The second joint campaign for the catwalk stars sees them cuddling up on set and modelling the seasonal styles inspired by gabardine .
The duo show off their razor-sharp cheekbones and flawless skin as they model the frames .